# Treat source files as text so a stray control byte (e.g. a NUL used as a Map-key
# delimiter) never makes git flag the whole file binary and hide its diff on GitHub.
# `text` = normalize eol; `diff` = always render a textual diff (overrides git's
# NUL-based binary auto-detection).
*.ts   text diff
*.mts  text diff
*.mjs  text diff
*.js   text diff
*.cjs  text diff
